msgid ""
"The advanced post search uses a set of tokens separated by spaces to filter "
"and sort the results. Below you will find a list of all the available tokens "
"and some examples of how to build a search query."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Each token may accept different operators and values. A token's supported "
"operators will be listed with the following search operator icons."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"The equality operator which indicates that returned posts will have the same "
"value as the token. Or, if the token supports wildcards, that all posts will "
"match the wildcard expression."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"The less than operator which indicates that returned posts will have a value "
"<em>less than</em> the token's value."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"The greater than operator which indicates that returned posts will have a "
"value <em>greater than</em> the token's value."
msgstr ""

msgid ""
"Some search tokens may accept wildcards in the specified search value. These "
"will make the filter more permissive, allowing resulting posts that match "
"where the wildcard(s) may be replaced with any value."
msgstr ""

